OL,3,CCompany fined after man run over by
OL,4,Ctruck on first day of work
OL,6,FCCTV footage of the incident, at the
OL,7,FMossdown Road site in Oldham was
OL,8,Freleased by the HSE on Wednesday, and
OL,9,Fshows the moment the man was hit.
OL,11,FThe man, now 44, suffered a bone
OL,12,Ffracture, as well as muscle and nerve
OL,13,Fdamage to his leg after being struck
OL,14,Fby the vehicle in July 2021.
OL,16,FIt happened on his first day as a
OL,17,Fwaste picker.
