OL,6,F"Vehicles such as shovel loaders
OL,7,Frequire plenty of space due to the
OL,8,Fnumber of blind spots and poor
OL,9,Fvisibility.
OL,11,F"This incident was easily avoidable by
OL,12,Fimplementing control measures and safe
OL,13,Fpractises.
