OL,3,CCompany fined after man run over by
OL,4,Ctruck on first day of work
OL,6,F"Measures should have been implemented
OL,7,Fto ensure that workers present in the
OL,8,Fyard were not put at risk from moving
OL,9,Fvehicles in and around where they were
OL,10,Fworking, including rigorous pedestrian
OL,11,Fand vehicle segregation and safe
OL,12,Frefuge for workers whilst vehicles are
OL,13,Foperating.
OL,15,F"This should be a reminder to the
OL,16,Fwaste industry of the need to ensure
OL,17,Fthat workplace transport is
OL,18,Fappropriately considered, with control
OL,19,Fmeasures introduced to ensure the
OL,20,Fappropriate separation of vehicles and
OL,21,Fpedestrians."
